parameters:
\SE[62]Everyone somehow made it out safely... but we went
through quite a ordeal.... \SE[81]Sigh... My clothes are all
soaked....

\SE[12]Girls shouldn't let their bodies get cold!
\!\SE[1]I'll start a fire right away...!

\SE[2]It seems like we were swept away quite a bit...
\!\SE[3]Is this place safe...\.I wonder?

\SE\SE[3]Yes! Of course...! \SE[3]Actually, the flow of this
river changes depending on the time. \SE[2]So even if we
follow the same route now, we might end up in a different
place.

\SE[15]Oh... what an amazing escape route.... \!\SE[16]A
professional's work... *clap clap*....

\SE[16]I'm honored to receive your praise! \SE[0]Vita-san,
you also made an amazing dive!

\SEWell... it was a job well done, Cat. \SE[3]The documents
are also okay, right?

\SM[nod]\SE[0]Yes, over here. \.We have perfect waterproof
measures...!

\SE[4]How is Laura doing? \!\SE[15]...She seems to have been
working hard.

\SE\SE[20]I think I'm starting to feel a little better.
\!\SE[20]But it seems like I'm still a bit dizzy...

\SE[2]Hmm...! Everyone shouldn't catch a cold! \SE[14]I'll
quickly start a fire...! I'll make sure to keep you warm!
